headline: Eversource: Q1 Earnings Snapshot
summary: SPRINGFIELD, Mass. AP) — Eversource Energy (ES) on Thursday reported first-quarter profit of $550.8 million. On a per-share basis, the Springfield, Massachusetts-based company said it had profit of $1.50.

headline: Eversource Energy Reports First Quarter 2025 Results
summary: HARTFORD, Conn. & BOSTON, May 01, 2025--Eversource Energy (NYSE: ES) today reported earnings of $550.8 million, or $1.50 per share, in the first quarter of 2025, compared with earnings of $521.8 million, or $1.49 per share, in the first quarter of 2024.
